<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            * {
                box-sizing: border-box;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .container {
                width: 100vw;
                height: 100vh;
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                background-color: #f6f9fc;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .container-mail-box {
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 40px 8px rgba(29,29,29,0.07);
                background-color: #fff;
                padding: 20px 50px;
                color: #7c869f;
                font-size: 0.9rem; 
                font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            }
            
            .mail-box-img {
                width: 300px;
                align-self: center;
            }

        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="container-mail-box">
                <img class="mail-box-img" src="https://preparame-backend.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/others/logo_preparame_home.png">
                <div>Ol√°! </div>
                <br>
                <div>Recebemos um pedido de agendamento para uma mentoria gratuita, segue os dados do solicitante:</div>
                <br>
                <div><b>Nome:</b>{{name}}</div>
                <div><b>E-Mail:</b>{{email}}</div>
                <div><b>Telefone:</b>{{phone}}</div>
                <div><b>Cargo:</b>{{position}}</div>
                <div><b>Empresa:</b>{{company}}</div>

                <br>
                <br>
                <div>
                    <h3>Equipe | <strong>Prepara.me</strong></h3>
                </div>
            </div>           
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
